WEBVTT

00:00:00.038 --> 00:00:05.710
Imagine if you live at the center
of a global conservation spotlight,

00:00:05.710 --> 00:00:08.254
but you have no voice.

00:00:08.671 --> 00:00:11.382
Your aspirations are not valid,

00:00:11.424 --> 00:00:13.843
and your knowledge does not count.

00:00:14.594 --> 00:00:19.098
Sadly, this happens very often in local
communities of key ecosystems

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:20.641
around the world.

